  "contentHtml": "\n    \n    \n        \n                <ul>\n                    \n                     <li><a href=\"/news/diagnostics\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Diagnostics</a></li>                     <li>1 min read</li>                 </ul>\n                            \n        \n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Mar 18, 2026 at 04:47 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure> New Delhi: <a href=\"/tag/redcliffe+labs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Redcliffe Labs</a> announced the appointment of <a href=\"/tag/dr.+sonal+saxena\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dr. Sonal Saxena</a> as Director – <a href=\"/tag/lab+operations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Lab Operations</a>, effective immediately, as part of its strategy to strengthen <a href=\"/tag/diagnostic+quality\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">diagnostic quality</a> and expand its <a href=\"/tag/preventive+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">preventive healthcare</a> capabilities.In her new role, Dr. Saxena will lead laboratory operations across the company’s nationwide network, with a focus on enhancing technical processes, quality systems, and accreditation standards.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->With over 25 years of experience in pathology and laboratory medicine, she brings expertise in clinical diagnostics, reference laboratory establishment, and operational leadership. She has previously worked with organisations such as Dr. Lal Path Labs, Apollo Clinic, Alchemist Hospital, and Diagno Labs.\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        A trained ISO 15189 assessor, Dr. Saxena has played a key role in securing NABL, CAP, and ISO accreditations in her earlier assignments.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->Commenting on the development, Aditya Kandoi, Founder and CEO, <a href=\"/tag/redcliffe+labs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Redcliffe Labs</a>, said diagnostics is increasingly becoming the first step in proactive healthcare, and the company remains focused on setting benchmarks in quality and accessibility.He added that Dr. Saxena’s experience in <a href=\"/tag/lab+operations\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lab operations</a> and accreditation will support the company’s expansion and help deliver reliable diagnostic services at scale.<!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->Dr. Saxena said Redcliffe Labs is contributing to a shift towards <a href=\"/tag/preventive+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">preventive healthcare</a> and added that she aims to further strengthen laboratory capabilities and processes to support early detection and improve health outcomes.                    \n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Mar 18, 2026 at 04:47 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Mar 18, 2026 at 04:47 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20